name: UW-Madison Lakeshore Nature Preserve Volunteer Opportunity
description: Help care for the Preserve. Learn about native ecosystems, meet new people, get exercise, and enjoy the outdoors! Training and tools provided. Groups and minors allowed with advance notice. Dress for outdoor work. Event will be canceled in case of rain. Meet at Picnic Point parking lot 129 (2004 University Bay Drive). On the 80 bus route.
locationAddress: Meet at Picnic Point parking lot (lot #129) on University Bay Drive. On the 80 bus route.
